ABOUT OUR MISSION
WE LOVE WINE!
We're here to bring people together over great wine—whether you're a seasoned wine nerd or just looking for a welcoming spot to enjoy a glass.
​
Our vibe is casual, fun, and inclusive. We offer a thoughtfully curated wine list, delicious bites like cheese plates, paninis, and house-made ice cream, and we host a bi-weekly blind tasting league that keeps things interesting.
​
At heart, we’re a community space with wine at the center—and we're always open to new ideas that make it even better.
Team Hummingbird
Mairin Moore - Proprietor
​
Mairin has worked in hospitality in Tallahassee for the last 12 years and is passionate about wine, cheese, and community involvement! She loves providing a welcoming atmosphere for people to learn about and enjoy wine and each other’s company. Mairin started on the CMS track, but has switched over to the WSET, and attempts to learn something new about wine every day! Her professional background includes fine dining service, management, bartending, catering, and private events. In her free time, you can catch her outside: gardening, on the water, foraging, or hiking. She also enjoys cooking, pairing wine and food, and generally discussing all things related to eating drinking, and traveling!
Erin Murphy - Operations Manager
​
Erin is a Tallahassee native who loves good food, music, and of course, wine! She spent three years working as the General Manager at a local wine shop/bar, where she helped teach deductive tasting classes to the public, curated by-the-glass wine menus, and hand selected every wine that was put onto the shelves. Erin is a huge wine nerd who loves sharing her knowledge and love of wine with others, and loves to take people outside of their wine comfort zone.
Aja Goodwin - Head Chef
​
​
Greg Hajcak - Founder of Hummingbird
​
Greg is a Professor of Psychology and Biomedical Sciences at Florida State University, where he studies the brain in relation to anxiety and depression. He is WSET Level 3 wine certified, and currently working on his WSET Level 4 Diploma. Greg oversees wine curation at Hummingbird, and hosts guided tastings.
"I’m excited to build a community around wine in Tallahassee.  I really love the social aspect of wine exploration - getting together to figure out what you do and do not like to drink, and discovering new wines to love." - Greg
Caitlyn Bradley - General Manager
​
​
